trans-unit.source: This event is raised by <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> when clicked.
trans-unit.target: Questo evento viene generato da <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>quando si fa clic.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>

trans-unit.source: The event is processed by the navigator (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) whose content contains the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>.
trans-unit.target: L'evento viene elaborato dallo strumento di spostamento (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>) il cui contenuto include <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>
